Takaka make big discovery! Maybe
discovery of century!!!

rows.label: tlk42100121_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Level of Cloud Sea rising! It true!
Takaka watching very carefully,
and see it shift!

rows.label: tlk42100121_02_msg0003

One sleep overnight and it in totally
different position!

rows.label: tlk42100121_02_msg0004
rows.name:
That mean not able to reach some
places any more...

rows.label: tlk42100121_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Takaka sure to win special award for
this! Could become honorary Nopon
of year! Ooh-hoo-hoo-hoo!!!
